Welcome to Smudge healing by Hem. This skill is designed to help you with everything you need to know about smudge healing. 

With Smudge healing, you can learn about how to perform smudge, what all can you smudge, what things do you require for smudging, the importance of smudging, prayers to chant while smudging, etc.
